item.description:
@3lv3n_snip3r wrote:

I see a post like this everyday on here. Just port forward your router (it’s different depending on your router) with the port your server is using. Also add that port to your firewall and your done. Very simple yet people don’t bother using google and try to apply themselves in this situation.
